 15:03 UPDATE – Three people are now confirmed dead after a head on collision involving two trucks. Department of Community Safety, Security and Liaison’s Zandile Mandlazi said both drivers and a passenger had died at the scene. “Two passengers who sustained serious injuries were rushed to a nearby hospital.” TRAC reported that the N4 near Komatipoort is still closed due to the incident. 14:37 KOMATIPOORT – Two people have been killed in an accident on the N4 near the town’s aerodrome. According to the Department of Community Safety, Security and Liaison’s Zandile Mandlazi, two vehicles were involved in the crash.  “So far the road is closed.” She said motorists are advised to use alternative routes. Lowvelder will update as soon as more information becomes available. 